{
  "uid": "v12-enterprise-whats-new",
  "title": "Grafana 12 \u2014 What's New (Enterprise Showcase)",
  "description": "Presentation-grade showcase of everything new in Grafana 12.0 through 12.4.3. Designed for an executive + engineering audience: business value on top, feature cards grouped by theme, live lab tiles to prove every feature is wired up, and deep links to the per-feature demo dashboards.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "enterprise",
    "showcase",
    "whats-new",
    "demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "ds_api",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Grafana API",
          "value": "grafana-api"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:2rem 1.5rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1f60c4 0%,#f2495c 50%,#ff9830 100%);border-radius:12px;color:#fff;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:.2em;opacity:.85;margin-bottom:.4rem\">OBSERVABILITY PLATFORM UPGRADE</div><div style=\"font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:.4rem\">Grafana 12.4.3 \u2014 what every team gets</div><div style=\"font-size:1.05rem;opacity:.95;max-width:1000px\">Four minor releases of new platform capability since 11.6.4. Drilldown suite GA, Git Sync for dashboards-as-code, SQL across any data source, managed recording rules, a new alert rule page, ad-hoc filters that actually stick, and the first public preview of dynamic dashboards with tabs + conditional rows.</div><div style=\"margin-top:1rem;display:flex;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap\"><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">12.0 Drilldowns GA</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">12.1 Regression transform</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">12.2 Ad-hoc filters GA</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">12.3 Panel time drawer</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">12.4 Git Sync + Dynamic dashboards</span></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Target version",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "grafana_build_info",
          "legendFormat": "{{version}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "/^version$/"
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "regex",
              "options": {
                "pattern": "^12\\.4\\..*$",
                "result": {
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "v12 features enabled",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/featuremgmt",
          "url_options": {
            "method": "GET"
          },
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "features",
          "columns": [
            {
              "selector": "enabled",
              "text": "enabled",
              "type": "boolean"
            }
          ],
          "filters": [
            {
              "field": "enabled",
              "operator": "equals",
              "value": [
                "true"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "count"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Data source types wired",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/datasources",
          "url_options": {
            "method": "GET"
          },
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": ""
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "count"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Angular panels (must be 0)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_api}",
        "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0",
          "url_options": {
            "method": "GET"
          },
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "",
          "columns": [
            {
              "selector": "angularDetected",
              "text": "angular",
              "type": "boolean"
            }
          ],
          "filters": [
            {
              "field": "angular",
              "operator": "equals",
              "value": [
                "true"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "count"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "noValue": "0"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 18,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#1f60c4\">\ud83d\udcca Query & Data</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.8rem\"><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #1f60c4;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(31,96,196,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">SQL Expressions <span style=\"background:#1f60c4;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">MySQL-dialect SELECT that joins two data sources in one panel. Stop building bash pipelines to correlate Prom metrics with Postgres rows.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-0-sql-expr\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #1f60c4;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(31,96,196,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Regression Transformation <span style=\"background:#1f60c4;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.1</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Linear or polynomial fit applied as a transform. Forecast memory / throughput several intervals ahead without any custom code.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-1-regression\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #1f60c4;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(31,96,196,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Ad-hoc Filters (GA) <span style=\"background:#1f60c4;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.2</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Redesigned filter UX. Any label, any value, every panel on the dashboard filters automatically \u2014 no query editing.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-2-adhoc\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #1f60c4;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(31,96,196,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Multi-property Variables <span style=\"background:#1f60c4;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">One display value can map to many query values. Finally solves <code>dev</code>/<code>development</code>, <code>prod</code>/<code>production</code> without two variables.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-4-multiprop\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #1f60c4;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(31,96,196,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Regex Variable Transforms <span style=\"background:#1f60c4;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Display the short name, query with the full path \u2014 regex on both <code>value</code> and <code>text</code>.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-4-regex-vars\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 18,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#f2495c\">\ud83d\udd0d Drilldowns & UX</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.8rem\"><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Drilldown Suite \u2014 GA <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Metrics, Logs, Traces and Profiles Drilldown now ship by default. One click from a panel to a faceted explore experience purpose-built for each signal type.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem;display:flex;gap:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap\"><a href=\"/a/grafana-metricsdrilldown-app\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">Metrics</a><span style=\"opacity:.4\">\u00b7</span><a href=\"/a/grafana-lokiexplore-app\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">Logs</a><span style=\"opacity:.4\">\u00b7</span><a href=\"/a/grafana-exploretraces-app\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">Traces</a><span style=\"opacity:.4\">\u00b7</span><a href=\"/a/grafana-pyroscope-app\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">Profiles</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">React Data Grid Table <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.0 \u2192 GA 12.2</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Table panel is now powered by react-data-grid: visibly faster on large tables, better column resize, grouping, gauge-in-cell, color backgrounds.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-0-table\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Panel Time Drawer <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.3</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Override the time range on any single panel from a little drawer \u2014 no more opening the full edit view to set <code>timeFrom</code>.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-3-time-drawer\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Redesigned Logs Panel <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.3</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Pattern recognition, smooth tail mode at 1000+ lines/s, inline column controls on the panel header.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-3-logs-panel\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Gauge Redesign \u2014 Circular + Arc <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">New <code>Style</code> option with Circular or Arc layout. Existing gauges auto-pick the closest match.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-4-gauge\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 18,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 30
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#ff9830\">\ud83d\udea8 Alerting & Reliability</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.8rem\"><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #ff9830;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Grafana-managed Recording Rules <span style=\"background:#ff9830;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Grafana can now evaluate recording rules itself. No need for a separate Mimir / Prometheus ruler for OSS \u2014 cheaper SLOs, simpler ops.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-0-recording-rules\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #ff9830;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">New Alert Rule Page \u2014 GA <span style=\"background:#ff9830;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.1</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Guided wizard, simplified routing, inline alert preview. Parity with Prometheus-managed rules via feature toggle.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-1-alert-rule-page\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #ff9830;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">HA Alertmanager cluster metrics <span style=\"background:#ff9830;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Cluster metrics renamed under a cleaner <code>grafana_alerting_ha_*</code> prefix. Your SLO dashboards need a rewrite \u2014 we have a helper for that.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-4-am-ha\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #ff9830;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Grafana Advisor <span style=\"background:#ff9830;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.1</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Built-in health scanner for plugins, data sources, SSO, dashboards. Run it before any change \u2014 it's a safety net.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/a/grafana-advisor-app\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 Open Advisor</a></div></div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 18,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 30
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#8f3bb8\">\ud83e\uddf0 Platform & Admin</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.8rem\"><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #8f3bb8;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(143,59,184,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Git Sync \u2014 Public Preview <span style=\"background:#8f3bb8;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Native GitOps for dashboards. Save drawer has a branch selector; every change lands as a PR. No more Terraform workarounds.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-0-git-sync\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #8f3bb8;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(143,59,184,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Dynamic Dashboards \u2014 Public Preview <span style=\"background:#8f3bb8;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">New layout engine: tabs, conditional rows, responsive grids. One dashboard can serve multiple audiences without dashboard-fanout.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-4-dynamic\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #8f3bb8;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(143,59,184,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Scenes Runtime \u2014 mandatory <span style=\"background:#8f3bb8;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Reactive dashboard runtime. Variable dependencies re-evaluate automatically; panel queries run only when their inputs change.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-0-scenes-vars\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #8f3bb8;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(143,59,184,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">Visualization Actions <span style=\"background:#8f3bb8;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.1</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">Attach custom actions to any panel. Click a stat \u2192 open a runbook URL with the failing instance's label values substituted in.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-1-viz-actions\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #8f3bb8;padding:.8rem 1rem;background:rgba(143,59,184,.06);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:1.05rem\">OTLP Log Defaults <span style=\"background:#8f3bb8;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.4rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.3rem\">OpenTelemetry structured attributes surface as first-class columns without expanding log rows.</div><div style=\"margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"/d/v12-4-otlp\" style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none\">\u2192 See the live demo</a></div></div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
