        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem 1.5rem;background:#0e1116;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #333;font-family:system-ui\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 .8rem 0\">\ud83c\udf93 For enterprise users \u2014 where to start</h3><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:.8rem\"><div><div style=\"color:#f2495c;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.3rem\">Analysts &amp; SREs</div>Open the <a href=\"/a/grafana-metricsdrilldown-app\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Metrics Drilldown</a> and try the <a href=\"/d/v12-2-adhoc\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">ad-hoc filter dashboard</a>. You will stop writing label selectors by hand.</div><div><div style=\"color:#1f60c4;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.3rem\">Data engineers</div>Try the <a href=\"/d/v12-0-sql-expr\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">SQL Expressions demo</a>. One panel can now correlate Prometheus, Postgres, Loki in a single SQL SELECT.</div><div><div style=\"color:#ff9830;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.3rem\">Platform / SRE team</div><a href=\"/d/v12-0-git-sync\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Git Sync</a> lets every dashboard change land as a reviewed PR \u2014 we already wired a CI workflow for it.</div><div><div style=\"color:#8f3bb8;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.3rem\">Leadership</div>Everything you see here is live data from the lab. The demo suite has <strong>16 feature dashboards</strong> and <strong>8 admin dashboards</strong> \u2014 all linked from the <a href=\"/d/v12-upgrade-overview\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Upgrade Overview</a>.</div></div></div>"
